snippet: Stephen Hill and Jeremy Kerley combined for four touchdowns, including a punt-return score by Kerley, in the victory over Buffalo.
abstract: New York Jets rookie recivers Stephen Hill and Jeremy Kerley make impressive debuts against the Buffalo Bills, scoring four touchdowns in the team's 48-28 victory.
lead_paragraph: Stephen Hill and Jeremy Kerley combined for four touchdowns, including a punt-return score by Kerley, in the victory over Buffalo.
